&nbsp;
Among the victims, a Mississippi woman, convinced in 2021 to invest little more than a million dollars in the Guardian Opportunity Management without being informed that the company's main investment vehicle, the Guardian Opportunity Fund, had recently lost 90% of its assets in management. Neither Williams told him he was going to use his money to pay other investors who were threatening legal actions against him.

